    "At the same time, BLR deformations may be studied in detail.",
    "In X-rays, almost all of the progress made in constraining the size of the corona, the inner disc radius, and the dark matter content of the lensing galaxies has been a result of the ability to determine the X-ray fluxes of each image of a lensed This task requires sub-arcsecond spatial resolution in X-rays, Chandra has been the only observatory with this capability.",
